'''Battle Group Serroco''', also known as the '''''Courageous'' battle group''', was a unit within the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]] that saw service during the [[Mandalorian Wars]] under the command of [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Saul Karath]]. Much of it was destroyed in the [[Battle of Serroco]], and the remainder came under heavy [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] attack in the retreat that was ordered shortly afterwards.

